ZH: 我今天要做一份数学卷子。
EN: I have to take a math test today.

ZH: 昨天老师发给我们一份英语卷子。
EN: Yesterday the teacher gave us an English test.

ZH: 他很用心地做完了卷子。
EN: He worked diligently to finish the test.

ZH: 我们每周都有一份化学卷子。
EN: We have a chemistry test every week.

ZH: 我们要把卷子交给老师。
EN: We have to hand in the test to the teacher.

ZH: 这是一份历史卷子，要好好复习哦。
EN: This is a history test, so make sure to review it well.

ZH: 没有参加课程，就无法做好卷子。
EN: Without attending the class, you won't be able to do well on the test.

ZH: 我不喜欢做卷子，觉得很累。
EN: I don't like doing tests, I find it tiring.

ZH: 她的卷子得了满分，真厉害！
EN: She got full marks on her test, she's amazing!

ZH: 一直不认真做卷子，成绩自然会很差。
EN: If you don't take the test seriously, your grade will naturally be poor.

ZH: 他花了两个小时来完成这份卷子。
EN: He spent two hours completing the test.

ZH: 我们必须用黑色墨水来写卷子。
EN: We have to use black ink to write the test.

ZH: 我们明天将会考一份地理卷子。
EN: We will have a geography test tomorrow.

ZH: 完成了卷子后，我们可以休息了。
EN: After finishing the test, we can take a break.

ZH: 做完卷子后，我觉得有点累了。
EN: I feel a bit tired after finishing the test.

ZH: 我的卷子上有很多错别字。
EN: There are many spelling mistakes in my test.

ZH: 为了做好卷子，我们必须认真复习。
EN: In order to do well on the test, we must review seriously.

ZH: 我每次都在考试结束后才发现错题在哪里。
EN: I always find out where my mistakes are only after the test is over.

ZH: 做完卷子后，我们还可以玩一会儿。
EN: After finishing the test, we can play for a while.

ZH: 我今天有三份卷子要做，好忙。
EN: I have three tests to take today, I'm so busy.
